Fine! Fine. Fine.
Fine, fine, fine, fine, fine, fine.

262
00:21:55,865 --> 00:21:58,764
Kill the bitch. Kill her with a knife.
Kill her with a knife!

263
00:21:58,866 --> 00:22:01,993
Kill the bitch. Kill the bitch.
Kill her with a knife.

264
00:22:02,101 --> 00:22:04,500
Put it in. Bitch!
Kill the bitch!

265
00:22:04,604 --> 00:22:06,627
Kill her!

266
00:22:14,543 --> 00:22:17,238
- You lookin' for some fun tonight, sweet thing?
- No, thank you.

267
00:22:17,345 --> 00:22:20,006
- Hey, man. Spare some change?
- No, not really.

268
00:22:20,113 --> 00:22:22,170
Hey, this looks okay.

269
00:22:22,281 --> 00:22:25,215
No, it doesn't.

270
00:22:25,316 --> 00:22:27,647
St. James, Josh. It's religious.

271
00:22:32,455 --> 00:22:36,355
Stay out there all night,
all day and all night again?

272
00:22:42,795 --> 00:22:46,593
- Hi.
- Hi.

273
00:22:50,499 --> 00:22:53,592
Uh, we would like
a hotel room, please.

274
00:22:53,701 --> 00:22:58,601
17.50 a night for the room,
$10 deposit for the sheets.

275
00:23:01,973 --> 00:23:04,030
Mm-hmm.

276
00:23:04,141 --> 00:23:06,267
You go straight
to the top of the stairs.

277
00:23:06,377 --> 00:23:09,936
The last door on the right,
next to the bathroom.

278
00:23:10,045 --> 00:23:13,138
Wait a second.
I'll show you.

279
00:23:16,349 --> 00:23:18,372
- It smells bad.
- Shh.

280
00:23:18,484 --> 00:23:20,747
- Have a pleasant stay.
- Thanks.

281
00:23:20,853 --> 00:23:24,150
Hey, Angel!
Get out of that bathroom now!

282
00:23:26,023 --> 00:23:28,354
He's in that bathroom all night.

283
00:23:29,858 --> 00:23:32,553
I don't want to stay here by myself.

284
00:23:32,660 --> 00:23:36,219
I can't help it, Josh.
I gotta be home by 10:00.

285
00:23:39,865 --> 00:23:41,922
Look, I'll cut classes tomorrow.

286
00:23:42,033 --> 00:23:46,661
We'll find that Zoltar thing
before you know it, okay?

287
00:23:46,770 --> 00:23:49,293
Just one night. All right?

288
00:23:49,404 --> 00:23:53,133
- All right.
- Good.

289
00:23:53,240 --> 00:23:56,730
- What if I can't sleep?
- It's probably better if you don't.

290
00:23:58,543 --> 00:24:00,600
See you in the morning.

291
00:24:00,711 --> 00:24:05,339
- Well, you know, like, what time?
- 8:30.

292
