I'd use the chain, if I were you.

293
00:24:12,419 --> 00:24:14,852
All right. Come on out.
Open the door.

294
00:24:14,954 --> 00:24:17,011
Stay away from here.

295
00:24:19,290 --> 00:24:24,055
If you don't have the money,
don't show us your face over here!

296
00:24:38,269 --> 00:24:41,101
Goddamn it!

297
00:24:48,443 --> 00:24:51,342
- Get out!
- Watch the money! Give me that!

298
00:26:05,292 --> 00:26:07,554
Mom. Mom.

