Five dollar filing charge.

321
00:27:17,056 --> 00:27:21,424
- See?
- One month to process. You get it in six weeks.

322
00:27:23,928 --> 00:27:28,329
- Six weeks?
- Sometimes longer, but you could get lucky.

323
00:27:28,430 --> 00:27:30,260
Next, please!

324
00:27:31,599 --> 00:27:33,657
Fill this out in triplicate.

325
