351
00:28:59,990 --> 00:29:02,822
- You can?
- Sure.

352
00:29:02,925 --> 00:29:06,882
- Hey, great. They use H.P. 3000s.
- You understand all that?

353
00:29:06,994 --> 00:29:10,156
Well, it's... It's an old system,
