361
00:29:38,681 --> 00:29:40,944
- I'll connect you.
- Are these the applications?

362
00:29:41,049 --> 00:29:43,915
- Yes. Just have a seat. I'll call your name.
- What's next?

363
00:29:44,018 --> 00:29:47,543
- There.
- Previous employment.

364
00:29:47,654 --> 00:29:51,321
- Your paper route.
- I don't think I can put that.

365
00:29:51,322 --> 00:29:54,313
- Neighborhood circulation director?
- Yeah!

366
00:29:54,425 --> 00:29:57,153
Yes. Hold on just a moment, please.

367
00:29:57,259 --> 00:30:00,455
What's he got?

368
00:30:02,863 --> 00:30:05,660
Hey, don't worry about it.

369
00:30:05,765 --> 00:30:08,061
Um, social security number?

370
00:30:08,167 --> 00:30:10,726
32-17-25.

371
00:30:10,835 --> 00:30:14,291
- What is that?
- It's my locker combination.

372
00:30:14,404 --> 00:30:18,065
- Great.
- Mr. Baskin?

373
00:30:18,173 --> 00:30:21,663
- Mr. Baskin?
- Y... Yes. Yes.

374
00:30:21,775 --> 00:30:24,868
The personnel director
will see you now.

375
00:30:26,578 --> 00:30:29,307
Uh, your son can wait out here.

376
00:30:32,782 --> 00:30:34,907
Yeah, okay.
Son, you should sit down.

377
00:30:35,017 --> 00:30:38,781
- And don't give the lady any trouble now.
- Sure, Dad.

378
00:30:38,886 --> 00:30:41,581
This way.

379
00:30:41,688 --> 00:30:44,781
Don't forget-
look him in the eye!

380
00:30:54,930 --> 00:30:58,523
