Where did you go to school?

387
00:31:21,047 --> 00:31:23,139
It was... It was called
George Washington.

388
00:31:23,248 --> 00:31:27,444
Oh, G.W. My brother-in-law
got his doctorate there.

389
00:31:29,219 --> 00:31:33,347
- Did you pledge?
