sometimes without a hyphen.

398
00:32:00,672 --> 00:32:04,127
Sometimes she spells the hyphen.

399
00:32:04,242 --> 00:32:06,941
Well, I really don't
know where I can put her.

400
00:32:06,966 --> 00:32:08,167
Put her on unemployment.

401
00:32:11,578 --> 00:32:14,875
- When can you start?
- Soon.

402
00:32:22,012 --> 00:32:24,206
MacMillan Toys. I'll transfer.

